Package: ruok
Title: R U OK - AI-Powered Data Analysis Assistant
Version: 0.1.0
Description: A Shiny application that transforms natural language prompts (Portuguese)
into executable R code for data analysis. The app integrates with AI models
(Zhipu GLM-4) to generate tidyverse/dplyr code, enabling spreadsheet users to
perform advanced data transformations, aggregations, and joins without programming
knowledge. Features include multi-file upload (CSV/Excel), interactive results
display, code transparency, and downloadable outputs.
